WEBVTT

00:07:59.037 --> 00:08:00.664
Listen for the loud and soft,

00:08:00.688 --> 00:08:02.498
the harmonic, the dissonant,

00:08:02.522 --> 00:08:06.331
and all the small details
that make every sound unique.

00:08:06.668 --> 00:08:11.831
Spend this time as mindful and focused
in this real-life sonic moment.

00:08:12.279 --> 00:08:15.831
Enjoy the magnificence
of hearing and listening.

00:08:16.331 --> 00:08:18.264
So here comes the first movement.

00:08:18.288 --> 00:08:19.621
Starting ...

00:08:19.645 --> 00:08:21.038
now.

00:08:21.062 --> 00:08:22.213
[I. Tacet]

00:08:22.237 --> 00:08:23.387
(No audio)